<Content>Average Average hotel far south of the city. Mainly business. On a main road, near to the trolley bus and there is a supermarket and restaurant across the way, but crossing the road is very very dangerous, be careful. Staff are okay, but absolutely no English. f you need to travel from the hotel take a taxi outside from one of the doorman,arrange a price first. Don't take the green/white taxis, too risky. 
